702
00:31:46,930 --> 00:31:49,230
Turns out your pain after the beating

703
00:31:49,350 --> 00:31:50,370
is all an act.

704
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:55,550
Your Majesty,

705
00:31:55,910 --> 00:31:57,410
aren't you going in?

706
00:31:57,490 --> 00:31:58,880
Let's go to Shoukang Palace.

707
00:31:58,880 --> 00:31:59,640
Yes.

708
00:32:01,610 --> 00:32:02,710
What?

709
00:32:03,130 --> 00:32:04,420
Really?

710
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:07,200
My apprentice saw it with his own eyes.

711
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:09,560
His Majesty left in anger.

712
00:32:10,450 --> 00:32:12,310
But it was quite a coincidence.

713
00:32:12,460 --> 00:32:16,230
Imperial Uncle was telling jokes to Her Highness at Fengluan Palace

714
00:32:16,230 --> 00:32:19,050
when His Majesty happened to see them.

715
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,740
It was that Ling'er.

716
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:24,570
My foolish son

717
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,900
is finally coming around.

718
00:32:29,570 --> 00:32:32,100
Even a foolish awakening is still awakening.

719
00:32:32,270 --> 00:32:33,100
But why

720
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,590
is Du Tianzhao

721
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:37,160
trying to curry favor with Consort Yue?

722
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,480
I really don't know.

723
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:40,490
Maybe

724
00:32:40,590 --> 00:32:42,880
he just wants to get closer to Her Highness.

725
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,630
His Majesty is here!

726
00:32:45,790 --> 00:32:46,830
Why are you here?

727
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:51,690
Greetings, Mother.

728
00:32:53,510 --> 00:32:54,140
You...

729
00:32:54,630 --> 00:32:55,540
Mother,

730
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:57,270
well...

731
00:32:57,520 --> 00:33:01,310
Minister Du is always at Fengluan Palace.

732
00:33:01,860 --> 00:33:03,480
It's bound to cause gossip in the harem,

733
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:04,520
don't you think?

734
00:33:04,630 --> 00:33:05,970
I remember

735
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:08,990
it was you who gave him the pass that

736
00:33:09,670 --> 00:33:11,670
allows free access to Fengluan Palace.

737
00:33:11,670 --> 00:33:13,430
If you think it's inappropriate,

738
00:33:13,430 --> 00:33:15,110
just take it back.

739
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,960
But I gave it to him with my own hands.

740
00:33:18,030 --> 00:33:20,030
How can I just take it back so easily?

741
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:21,770
That would be so humiliating.

742
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,950
Alright, alright.

743
00:33:24,970 --> 00:33:26,250
I'm getting old.

744
00:33:26,280 --> 00:33:28,310
I can't handle these kinds of things anymore.

745
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:29,240
Besides,

746
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,280
Consort Yue is pregnant.

747
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:32,960
You should focus all your attention on her,

748
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:33,660
right?

749
00:33:33,690 --> 00:33:36,500
Stop keeping your eyes on the Imperial Uncle.

750
00:33:37,650 --> 00:33:38,920
I'm just trying to...

751
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:39,640
Alright.

752
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:40,920
You're a grown man.

753
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:43,070
You should be devoted to Consort Yue.

754
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:45,310
Yes.

755
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:47,700
Stop overthinking everything else.

756
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,370
Am I...

757
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:51,030
devoted to Consort Yue?

758
00:33:54,210 --> 00:33:56,250
[Yongqian Palace]

759
00:33:56,250 --> 00:33:57,190
Yue Chi?

760
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:00,790
Your Majesty.

761
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:03,570
What happened to you?

762
00:34:04,370 --> 00:34:05,640
Please don't ask.

763
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:08,929
I was just taught a painful lesson.

764
00:34:12,560 --> 00:34:13,820
By a woman?

765
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:15,460
Well,

766
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,440
you could say that.

767
00:34:23,389 --> 00:34:24,889
Take care of yourself.

768
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:33,210
The Yue siblings are quite interesting.

769
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:37,280
How's that 100-day plan of Consort Yue's

770
00:34:37,489 --> 00:34:38,650
coming along?

771
00:34:43,469 --> 00:34:45,530
Once I develop the new fragrance,

772
00:34:45,590 --> 00:34:48,060
I'll definitely invite the sisters over to try it.

773
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:49,920
This fabric is common,

774
00:34:50,030 --> 00:34:53,480
but the thread and stitching are exquisite.

775
00:34:53,500 --> 00:34:55,630
You've put in a lot of effort, Lady Xia.

776
00:34:56,310 --> 00:34:57,880
Thank you, Your Majesty.

777
00:34:57,990 --> 00:35:00,320
What's Consort Hui been busy with lately?

778
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:02,840
Consort Yue said she's good with numbers,

779
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,510
so she's been helping manage the accounts.

780
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,150
Your Highness,

781
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:06,280
stop looking at the harem's accounts.

782
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,710
Focus on our palace's instead.

783
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:09,030
