784
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,240
It doesn't matter.

785
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,800
Ask the family for more money.

786
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:12,400
Oh, right.

787
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:14,160
Lady Lan's flute is quite worn out.

788
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:16,310
I have a jade quota from my rank, right?

789
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:16,970
Give it to her.

790
00:35:16,970 --> 00:35:17,750
Also,

791
00:35:17,780 --> 00:35:18,710
check if Yingwan

792
00:35:18,720 --> 00:35:20,190
still has enough incense.

793
00:35:20,230 --> 00:35:21,430
If not, send her some.

794
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:27,250
The floral fragrance enchants the air,

795
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:29,620
while nature's own scent mingles there.

796
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:32,590
This fragrance is truly wonderfully blended.

797
00:35:32,610 --> 00:35:35,320
We should thank you for giving us this opportunity.

798
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,320
Otherwise, with the Palace Fragrance Department and Cloth Department,

799
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:39,920
how could we have the chance to do these things?

800
00:35:40,730 --> 00:35:42,320
And Qu, thank you

801
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:44,980
for bringing me such excellent fragrant herbs.

802
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,390
Alright.

803
00:35:46,510 --> 00:35:48,370
I know you've arranged this well.

804
00:35:48,390 --> 00:35:50,660
Get started and show us.

805
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,400
Yes.

806
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:56,150
Why are they closing the windows?

807
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:58,490
It's not only to prevent the fragrance from dispersing

808
00:35:58,490 --> 00:36:00,190
but also to avoid attracting bees and insects

809
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:02,790
that could harm everyone if it gets too strong.

810
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,680
You're so thoughtful.

811
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,960
When the incense charcoal burns and releases

812
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,670
the sandalwood scent inherent to the charcoal itself,

813
00:36:09,670 --> 00:36:11,590
that means it's successfully infused.

814
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:15,110
Then we can cut the incense and prepare to burn it.

815
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:18,960
It smells so good.

816
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:19,440
Oh my!

817
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:19,960
It's really fragrant.

818
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:21,220
It really is fragrant.

819
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,840
Can you teach us how to make it in the future?

820
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,630
Sure.

821
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:27,090
Can we make it into sachets?

822
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:30,920
If we put the sachets on clothes, it would definitely smell wonderful.

823
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,870
Can it be made into sachets?

824
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,090
I can try.

825
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,020
Okay.

826
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:57,150
Something's not right.

827
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:58,110
Yue.

828
00:36:59,940 --> 00:37:00,800
Yue.

829
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:13,170
Wake up.

830
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:14,380
Wake up.

831
00:37:14,970 --> 00:37:15,820
Wake up!

832
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:18,100
Let me help you up.

833
00:37:18,430 --> 00:37:20,310
Why is the smoke so thick?

834
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:23,230
Why is it so choking?

